{"tid":265182,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"全球狂賀雲加續約","createTime":"2017-05-31T12:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T12:57:14.000Z","uid":16659,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35f5c49cb19979c9b7589a0c71a3b1f16f2f4762","tid":265182,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"Club and Wenger agree contract extension<br />\n<br />\nArsenal Football Club and Ars&egrave;ne Wenger have agreed a two-year extension to his contract as manager.<br />\n<br />\nAnnouncing the news, our majority owner Stan Kroenke said: &ldquo;Our ambition is to win the Premier League and other major trophies in Europe. It&rsquo;s what the fans, players, staff, manager and board expect and we won&rsquo;t rest until that is achieved. Ars&egrave;ne is the best person to help us make that happen. He has a fantastic track record and has our full backing.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nArs&egrave;ne and chief executive Ivan Gazidis have conducted a full review of our on and off the pitch activities to identify areas for improvement to build a sustained title challenge.<br />\n<br />\nArs&egrave;ne, who lifted the FA Cup for a record-breaking seventh time on Saturday, said: &ldquo;I love this club and I am looking forward to the future with optimism and excitement. We are looking at what we do well and how we can be stronger everywhere. This is a strong group of players and with some additions we can be even more successful. We&rsquo;re committed to mounting a sustained league challenge and that will be our focus this summer and next season.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I am grateful to have the support of the board and Stan in doing everything we can to win more trophies. It&rsquo;s what we all want and I know it&rsquo;s what our fans around the world demand.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nIn addition to the record &pound;110m investment in players last summer, we have made almost &pound;40 million investment in facilities at our London Colney training centre and the Academy at Hale End in the last two years.<br />\n<br />\nIvan said: &ldquo;There is no complacency anywhere at this club. Our goal is to compete for and win trophies here and in Europe. Everything we do is designed to make that happen and we will be working hard on and off the pitch this summer to improve and make a strong challenge next season. The club has grown beyond recognition in every aspect in recent years and we have the platform to be successful and meet the ambitions we and our fans share.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/20170531/club-and-wenger-agree-contract-extension\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.arsenal.com%2Fnews%2Fnews-archive%2F20170531%2Fclub-and-wenger-agree-contract-extension&d=CVBbksuk%2FbBim1Jn98wMFU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=fa09c4fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.arsenal.com/news/news-archive/20170531/club-and-wenger-agree-contract-extension</a><br />\n<br />\n雲加<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da519c506fd777da810aff04d9731109d550b99f","tid":265182,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://31.media.tumblr.com/bc94389c3d62566c450c5564c4d09a97/tumblr_ngmhm76sFh1tp5565o1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F31.media.tumblr.com%2Fbc94389c3d62566c450c5564c4d09a97%2Ftumblr_ngmhm76sFh1tp5565o1_400.gif&h=96a87d84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"210982acef0c7cb172087046311453fed24c539b","tid":265182,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"雲加永續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab681c6a0653af2b26c74e248fa113a4619c1921","tid":265182,"uid":97997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"Arsene會永遠都存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cdb8c66de70fbcd6a83958a8a15d3109f1dbd9","tid":265182,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://31.media.tumblr.com/bc94389c3d62566c450c5564c4d09a97/tumblr_ngmhm76sFh1tp5565o1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F31.media.tumblr.com%2Fbc94389c3d62566c450c5564c4d09a97%2Ftumblr_ngmhm76sFh1tp5565o1_400.gif&h=96a87d84&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca1fd9ce736f4426154961bc7a49c95279a7ca4","tid":265182,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://31.media.tumblr.com/bc94389c3d62566c450c5564c4d09a97/tumblr_ngmhm76sFh1tp5565o1_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F31.media.tumblr.com%2Fbc94389c3d62566c450c5564c4d09a97%2Ftumblr_ngmhm76sFh1tp5565o1_400.gif&h=96a87d84&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n吸煙大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8aab549428f15d1287280d8f39c6d0164f7fb6","tid":265182,"uid":116311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"恭賀其餘英超球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad4a5f71cf8b97996acf36718a4a78f26c517e9","tid":265182,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c